<h4>Borders Options</h4>

<ol>

<li>Make sure the <strong>Borders Tab</strong> is selected.</li>
<li>Choose the type of border. Notice that you can choose the style, color, and width of the border in the center panel.</li>
<li>Choose whether to apply the border to the <strong>text</strong> or to the <strong>paragraph</strong> under the <strong>Apply to:</strong> box.</li>
<li>Click Ok.</li>
</ol>

 <img class="img-wrap style1" src=
            "images/wordprocessing/borderbox.jpg" alt="">

<hr>
