<h4>Shading Options</h4>

<ol>

<li>Make sure the <strong>Shading Tab</strong> is selected.</li>
<li>Choose Fill Color. Notice that you can see the percentage of color when you hover over the color with your mouse.</li>
<li>Choose whether to apply the shading to the <strong>text</strong> or to the <strong>paragraph</strong> under the <strong>Apply to:</strong> box.</li>
<li>Click Ok.</li>
</ol>

 <img class="img-wrap style1" src=
